data.name: Men's Instant Photochromic Sunglasses, Polarized and Photochromic Sports Sunglasses, Ultra Lightweight, Asian Fit, UV Protection, UV400 Protection, Polarized Lenses, Photochromic Lenses, Case Included, Ideal for Golf, Running, Basebal
data.short_description:
Handling Precautions

This product uses LCD photochromic lenses. Handle it with care, just like a precision instrument.

To prevent damage to the LCD lenses, please observe the following precautions.


Always carry the product in the included hard case. Subjecting

the lenses to strong impacts or pressure may cause malfunction.

Even if the product is in the case, dropping it can damage the LCD lenses.


Do not leave the product in a car. Leaving it in high temperatures or in environments with large temperature fluctuations may cause malfunction.

Be especially careful not to leave the product in a car, even for a short time, in summer.


Forcibly bending the lenses can damage the LCD.

Opening the temples too far can also cause severe strain on the lenses.

Do not forcibly bend or twist the frame or lenses.
